<item>
            <title>[LU-18174] endless lfsck if osd_iget2 returns an error</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18174</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;lfsck falls into endless loop in osd_check_lmv() if osd_iget2() returns error:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
